1. Check if an given integer is even or odd
    The expression (n&1) will return value 1 or 0
    depending upon n is odd or even.

    1st example

        16 --> 10000  &
        1  --> 00001
            -----------
               00000
    2nd example
        17 --> 10001  &
        1  --> 00001
            ------------
               00001

    